o the AP.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"score\": 0.9999686344821009, \"rank\": 3.1366501605818565e-05, \"text\": \"Waterkloof\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\"}, {\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.903744053027734e-16, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oscar Pistorius in the High Court in Pretoria, South Africa, Wednesday, June 15, 2016.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.003984669100804e-31, \"text\": \"Oscar Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.999999375616166, \"rank\": 6.243425525318563e-07, \"text\": \"High Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0563031180179275e-18, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}, {\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.04